## 💳 Pricing Plans

| Plan | Price | Features |
|------|-------|----------|
| **Free** | ₦0/month | • 1 plan per month • Basic text export • Standard templates |
| **Basic** | ₦15,000/month | • Unlimited plans • PDF + text export • Save & edit projects • Email support |
| **Professional** | ₦45,000/month | • All Basic features • Advanced design options • Cost estimation • Priority support • Custom modifications • API access |

---

## 💳 Payment Methods Supported

- **Debit/Credit Cards** — Visa, Mastercard, Verve, American Express
- **Bank Transfers** — Direct account-to-account (UBA, GTBank, Zenith, etc.)
- **Mobile Money** — Paga, OPay, PalmPay, Moniepoint
- **USSD Codes** — *123#1# for Airtel Money, *901*1# for MTN Mobile Money
- **Cryptocurrency** — Bitcoin, Ethereum (via Coinbase Commerce)

All payments processed securely via [Paystack](https://paystack.com) with PCI DSS compliance.

