## 📝 Customization Guide

### Change Brand Colors

Edit `src/config/branding.js`:

```javascript
export const BRAND_COLORS = {
  primary: '#1E2952',      // HARZ navy
  secondary: '#D4AF37',    // HARZ gold
  accent: '#4B6268',       // Accent gray
  success: '#10B981',      // Green
  warning: '#F59E0B',      // Amber
  error: '#EF4444'         // Red
};
```

Update CSS variables in `public/styles.css`:
```css
:root {
  --color-primary: #1E2952;
  --color-secondary: #D4AF37;
  --color-accent: #4B6268;
}
```

### Modify Pricing Plans

Edit `src/config/pricing.js`:

```javascript
export const PRICING_PLANS = [
  {
    id: 'free',
    name: 'Free',
    price: 0,
    currency: 'NGN',
    features: ['1 plan/month', 'Text export']
  },
  {
    id: 'basic',
    name: 'Basic',
    price: 15000,
    currency: 'NGN',
    features: ['Unlimited plans', 'PDF export', 'Save projects']
  }
];
```

### Add New Project Templates

Create `src/templates/projectTypes.js`:

```javascript
export const PROJECT_TEMPLATES = {
  residential: {
    name: 'Residential House',
    description: 'Single/multi-family dwelling',
    defaultFields: ['rooms', 'bathrooms', 'garage', 'garden']
  },
  commercial: {
    name: 'Commercial Building',
    description: 'Office, retail, warehouse',
    defaultFields: ['floors', 'occupancy', 'parking', 'loading_dock']
  },
  // Add more templates...
};
```

### Customize AI Prompts

Edit `src/config/ai.js`:

```javascript
export const AI_SYSTEM_PROMPT = `You are an expert Nigerian construction consultant...
Follow NBC (Nigerian Building Code) standards...
Provide detailed technical specifications...`;

export const AI_MODEL_CONFIG = {
  model: 'gpt-4-turbo',
  temperature: 0.7,
  max_tokens: 2000,
  top_p: 0.9
};
```

